Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:07.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,Mail's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.43,0:00:11.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Please be a "yes", please be a "yes"! Please be a '"yes"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:14.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She can make it! She can make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:18.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,Going out on a limb here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:22.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,but I'm guessing that Princess Cadance said she can come this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:25.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm finally gonna get to spend some quality time with my sister-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:28.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is the best news ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:33.32,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,So sorry for barging in like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.32,0:00:36.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,but I'm so excited, I just couldn't wait to tell somepony!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:43.15,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,The Equestrian Society for the preservation of rare creatures has given me permission
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:47.48,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,to observe the rarest tiniest most adorable magical creatures in all of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:49.30,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,The Breezies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wow, Fluttershy! That's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:54.76,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's not just fantastic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:57.76,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,it just might be the best news ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:05.88,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I've just got the most incredible mail anypony has ever received in all of recorded pony postal history!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.88,0:01:10.60,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's a flyer about a one day sell-out of used patio furniture!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.24,0:01:13.35,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Could this day get any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{commercials}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:03.82,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Here's a wrap in case it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:08.41,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And I packed you a basket of nice fresh apples in case you get hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:09.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Have a great time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:13.80,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, I will! And I hope you have fun with Cadance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:16.58,Somepony,,0,0,0,,All aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:21.91,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:24.23,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:25.65,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:30.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.62,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, something floaty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit nervous about Cadance's visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:42.98,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What could you be nervous about, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:45.23,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Cadance just loves you to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:48.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know. But I really want her visit to go without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:50.71,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:55.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, the last few times we've seen each other haven't exactly been worry-free.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:03:00.06,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The fate of Equestria has hung in the balance during most of your visits with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:01.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Cadance and I haven't really had a chance to just enjoy being friends again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:09.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Which is why it's so important that this visit be about the two of us having some real quality time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:12.46,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing you've got a plan that will keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The timing couldn't be more perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:17.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,For one day only! Right here in Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Star Swirl The Bearded travelling museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:23.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Cadance and I can spend the whole day looking at Star Swirl The Bearded artifacts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:27.10,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a perfect drama-free way to spend the day with Cadance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:31.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not counting the drama surrounding which of the bells from his cloak they've chosen to put on display —
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:34.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spoiler alert! It's this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:39.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Something in my throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.02,0:03:41.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Like a big ball of lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I think it sounds delightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:47.83,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yep. Definitely sounds like you two will have some real quality time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Just quiet time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:08.86,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.15,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,I'm teasing, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:17.34,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,We're sisters-in-law, we don't have to be so formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:26.81,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Knowing you, you've made some plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:28.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Boy, have I.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:30.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hang on just one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:30.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You, guys…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:33.73,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't you worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:38.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We will make sure that nothing but nothing interferes with your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:41.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Go on, have a hooternanny with your kinfolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You really are the best friends a pony could ever have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:46.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Coming, Cadance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:51.62,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Two sisters-in-law bonding…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:55.16,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Well, I for one am gonna make sure that nothing spoils their day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.93,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:04:59.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Duck!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:04.00,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Rarity, that doesn't look anything like a duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:14.06,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, not a "what", but a "who", dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.11,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:17.59,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That sounds like…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:23.51,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Discord!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{commercials}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.87,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What in tarnation are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.42,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And why the jumping June bugs are you blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:36.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,More like a shade of cerulean, to be precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:39.12,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Whatever color you are, it's the color of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:43.45,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh Rainbow Dash, I've changed, surely you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:46.75,Discord,,0,0,0,,I was reformed by lovely little…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.37,Discord,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What are you? Sick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.47,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, of course I'm sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:06:00.12,Discord,,0,0,0,,The blue skin, these sneezes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:02.92,Discord,,0,0,0,,Could somebody find me a fainting couch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:06.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:12.32,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, charming, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:14.65,Discord,,0,0,0,,I can't stop sneezing and wheezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:17.95,Discord,,0,0,0,,In short, I need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:22.30,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,If you're so sick, why have you come here instead of,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:26.34,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,you know, staying home in bed and getting over your weird illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:35.20,Discord,,0,0,0,,Because this condition has left me helpless, simply helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:40.00,Discord,,0,0,0,,Why, I can barely lift a spoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:50.07,Discord,,0,0,0,,I came to find the one pony who truly understands me and could nurse me back to health.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.62,Discord,,0,0,0,,Where is that dear sweet Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:56.75,Discord,,0,0,0,,I need attention. I need some care. I need…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You need to chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:07:00.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:01.80,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.25,Discord,,0,0,0,,Her trip to see the breezies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:05.67,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. I had forgotten that that was today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:08.16,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,How do you know about her trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:11.30,Discord,,0,0,0,,She told me about it. In her last letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.75,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You and Fluttershy write each other letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.75,0:07:17.55,Discord,,0,0,0,,Of course we do. We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:23.47,Discord,,0,0,0,,It's just such a shame that today of all days is when I really need her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:25.62,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:26.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Good thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:31.15,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Head on home, put your feet up, I'm sure eventually you'll have the strength to make yourself soup or something
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:37.67,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, no-no-no-no, I mean, while she's gone, you ponies can take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:42.00,Discord,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what friends are for, taking care of each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.52,Discord,,0,0,0,,Let the healing begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:46.90,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:51.82,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, that's some way to treat a suffering friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.25,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.45,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'll give you cuddles and read stories and tell you all about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.27,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I was born on a tuesday…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.45,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're so sweet to offer,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:07.55,Discord,,0,0,0,,but Rarity and Applejack already volunteered to be my own personal nursemaids.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:08.97,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:12.72,Discord,,0,0,0,,I so hope you don't mind, Pinkie Pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:15.60,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Well, as a matter of fact, I most certainly…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:19.50,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Heeey! Who keeps throwing away these perfectly good baloons?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:22.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That joker is up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:26.94,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And whatever it is, we're gonna keep it as far away from Twilight and Princes Cadance as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:32.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You're right. We promised we wouldn't let anything ruin their visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:36.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Although I do so wish that anything had turned out to be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:43.05,Discord,,0,0,0,,Did I hear you two talking about Princess Cadance's visit with Princess Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:44.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:48.65,Discord,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy had mentioned that those two were getting together today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.30,Discord,,0,0,0,,How wonderful for them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.25,Discord,,0,0,0,,It is so rare that those two get to see one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:57.05,Discord,,0,0,0,,I don't know about you, but I sometimes wonder how close they could actually be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:09:01.20,Discord,,0,0,0,,All those years apart before being reunited.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.92,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,They're plenty close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:08.22,Discord,,0,0,0,,And if they're not, this rare opportunity to focus on their friendship will certainly bring them closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:09.07,Discord,,0,0,0,,Unless…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:10.32,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.32,0:09:11.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They mustn't be disturbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.42,Discord,,0,0,0,,Disturb them? Why, wouldn't dream of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:19.10,Discord,,0,0,0,,Not when I have two such dear friends on my own, who have already offered to take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.77,Discord,,0,0,0,,And at such peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.55,0:09:24.37,Discord,,0,0,0,,This flu of mine is highly…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.75,Discord,,0,0,0,,Contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.12,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.02,Discord,,0,0,0,,I've gotten you both sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:40.75,Discord,,0,0,0,,Whom ever shall I turn to now, in my time of need?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:47.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A whole day to celebrate Starswirl the Bearded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What could be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:51.55,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:57.22,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Is that the candlestick he used to light the way when he was exploring the caverns of Maretania?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:58.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.80,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Oh, I cannot believe I'm getting to see it in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:14.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Discord, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:18.78,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear dear princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.81,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to say that I'm sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:24.72,Discord,,0,0,0,,Blue flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.36,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Blue flu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:29.91,Discord,,0,0,0,,I fear I've already given it to poor Applejack and Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:36.75,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Magic health bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Good thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.05,Discord,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:42.86,Discord,,0,0,0,,How would Twilight nurse me back to health, if she was sick too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:46.58,Discord,,0,0,0,,You will be letting me stay at your place until I'm all better, wont you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:49.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Stay? With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Now is not really the best time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:53.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Though I'm sure you already knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:58.45,Discord,,0,0,0,,But taking in the sick and the desperate, isn't that what Fluttershy would do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:02.88,Discord,,0,0,0,,Isn't helping something that friends do for friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:08.46,Discord,,0,0,0,,Unless, of course, you are really saying that you are not my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, that is not what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:15.38,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, how elated I am to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.78,Discord,,0,0,0,,Shall the three of us head back to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:21.92,Discord,,0,0,0,,I dont want to get anypony else sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Guess we don't have much choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:26.40,Discord,,0,0,0,,Carry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:31.52,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,It isn't far. I think you can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:40.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Need anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:42.65,Discord,,0,0,0,,Just knowing that I have a good friend like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:46.79,Discord,,0,0,0,,To take care of me, has made me feel better already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:49.89,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine here on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:58.29,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oh, just before you go, just a little small request.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:01.61,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,It's going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:05.94,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,We'll just get him what he wants and be back to the exhibit in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:07.59,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,What was it that you needed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:10.06,Discord,,0,0,0,,A little glass of water, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:12.40,Discord,,0,0,0,,A fresh-pressed hanky if I sneeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.82,Discord,,0,0,0,,Some tea with honey from the bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.01,Discord,,0,0,0,,Whenever you can brew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.01,0:12:18.16,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,I'll get your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:20.42,Discord,,0,0,0,,And while I get a little rest
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.92,Discord,,0,0,0,,A teeny tiny small request
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:25.28,Discord,,0,0,0,,Some codfish oil for my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.33,Discord,,0,0,0,,Poured from a crystal cruet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:28.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A crystal cruet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:31.54,Discord,,0,0,0,,My goodness I'm an nincompoop \NBecause I fear I got the croup
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:34.80,Discord,,0,0,0,,I need a vat of pumpkin soup \N And scarves made out of zinnias.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:38.05,Discord,,0,0,0,,Did I say "zinnias"? I meant silk, \N Or something shiny of that ilk
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:41.12,Discord,,0,0,0,,And then I'll need some nice warm milk \N And pastry from Abyssinia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:44.07,Discord,,0,0,0,,And since my stomach's feeling crummy \N Why not give my aching tummy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:47.15,Discord,,0,0,0,,Something soothing, something yummy \N Piled up with noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:49.99,Discord,,0,0,0,,And a slice of homemade rye \N With stacks of swiss way up high
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:53.35,Discord,,0,0,0,,Served with sides of sweet mince pie More basil; I need oodles
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:13:01.43,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'll be grateful for your charity \N Until the bitter end
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:08.45,Discord,,0,0,0,,Because I've heard that tenderness \N Is what you lend an ailing friend
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:11.14,Discord,,0,0,0,,Tenderness, isn't that right, friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Right, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:12.75,Discord,,0,0,0,,So!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:15.17,Discord,,0,0,0,,Who's ready for my big reprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:18.25,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'd like that glass of water please, \N Some magic spell to cure disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:21.29,Discord,,0,0,0,,A firm "gesundhoof" when I sneeze, \N A fresh bouquet of roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:24.55,Discord,,0,0,0,,Some lozenges will soon appease \N My wheezing when I start to sneeze
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.70,Discord,,0,0,0,,A wig to keep me from the breeze \N And blankets for my toes-es.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.58,Discord,,0,0,0,,Take tweezers out of my valise \N And then massage my knobby knees
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:33.29,Discord,,0,0,0,,A bowl of peas, some extra cheese\N A cuddle with a Pekingese
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:36.23,Discord,,0,0,0,,A singing harp who's named Louise \N A goat on skis, a new trapeze
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:40.74,Discord,,0,0,0,,And more and more and more and more of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:42.43,Discord,,0,0,0,,And just because I oughta…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:47.51,Discord,,0,0,0,,Make sure I'm drinking in the right \N Amount of fluids day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.09,Discord,,0,0,0,,I wish I may, I wish I might
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:52.02,Discord,,0,0,0,,Have just one little thing \N Oh, would you please finally bring me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:14:00.44,Discord,,0,0,0,,That tiny glass of water?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:10.52,Discord,,0,0,0,,Oops, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Allright, this is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:16.46,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,How did you even catch this flu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.65,Discord,,0,0,0,,Inadequate hoof-and-claw washing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:20.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There must be some way to just cure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:23.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,There has to be a spell or a remedy in one of my books.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:25.70,Discord,,0,0,0,,There is one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:28.98,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,And you didn't think to mention it earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:30.74,Discord,,0,0,0,,Slipped my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:36.85,Discord,,0,0,0,,On the hill at the very edge of Equestria there grows an equisite magic flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:40.31,Discord,,0,0,0,,Pick the flower as it drops its petals at sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:45.04,Discord,,0,0,0,,Then you can make a magical soothing elixir to cure the blue flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:52.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I suppose you had/have a good reason you didn't bother to go get this flower as soon as you realised you're sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:54.97,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well I couldn't travel that far in my condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:59.73,Discord,,0,0,0,,By the time I got there I'd be too weak to even attempt to retrieve the flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:03.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So, where exactly are Cadance and I headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:08.37,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, you want to head north, turn left… Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:12.87,Discord,,0,0,0,,You know… It would be much easier if I took you there myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:16.47,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,I thought you were in no condition to travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:20.49,Discord,,0,0,0,,I'm not, we will need to make some arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{commercials}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:31.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Doing OK there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:35.74,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,To be honest I'm a little out of practice when it comes to flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:38.43,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, then lucky for you we are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:45.35,Discord,,0,0,0,,It's just at the top of that hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:54.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was for us to have some peaceful quality time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:58.05,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,I know, I was looking forward to it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:06.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is the top, but where is that flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:18.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on, if we hurry we can still have some time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:29.09,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,One. Last. Pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Let's get Discord and this flower back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:38.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,- Then all our problems are solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.25,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,- What in Equestria!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:03.57,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Twilight, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:06.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Get your coils off my sister in law!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:21.45,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Let go of my sister in law.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:23.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:24.89,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Don't thank me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:38.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:43.49,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,And for good measure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.51,0:17:50.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:54.78,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Yes, better than OK actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Then let's get Discord back to Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:18:01.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,make that elixir and finally get a chance to spend some quality time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:09.56,Discord,,0,0,0,,To the ends of Equestria to face such great danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:14.34,Discord,,0,0,0,,And she did it for me, she did it all for me, for me, for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:23.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You were faking!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:27.06,Discord,,0,0,0,,I was, but I had a very good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We're listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:35.39,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, I was in my "Thinking Tree", that's where I do most of my really deep thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:37.27,Discord,,0,0,0,,I was there and I said to myself, I said:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:41.26,Discord,,0,0,0,,"Discord, your friend Twilight says that she is your pal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:44.94,Discord,,0,0,0,,but she never writes and she never pops in for a visit"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:46.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I don't even know where you li…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:51.50,Discord,,0,0,0,,Now that she's a princess, maybe she has decided that she is too good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:53.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I have never considered myself too…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:57.89,Discord,,0,0,0,,But how was I supposed to know for sure that I'm truly still friends
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.52,Discord,,0,0,0,,with one of the most important ponies around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:01.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm not more im…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:06.52,Discord,,0,0,0,,By seeing if you would go to the ends of Equestria for me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:13.75,Discord,,0,0,0,,Which you did. Literally. Congratulations, Twilight, you passed my friendship test.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:23.55,Discord,,0,0,0,,Why the angry eyes? You love passing tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:28.05,Discord,,0,0,0,,It's not because my little exam put a dampfer on your visit with Princess Cadance, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:33.49,Discord,,0,0,0,,Made it so that there was no time for you two to focus on your friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:36.39,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,You didn't put a dampfer on our visit at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:37.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,- He didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:37.90,Discord,,0,0,0,,- I didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:42.43,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Spending the day at the "Starswirl the Bearded" exhibit would have been more relaxing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:46.27,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,but to be honest, relaxation is the last thing I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:51.33,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong, life in the Crystal Empire is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:55.20,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,But it has become a little predictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:58.24,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,I enjoy a little excitement now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:01.96,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Getting to face all these challenges today was just what I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:05.18,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,And  facing them with you just made me realise even more
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:08.61,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,how lucky I am to  have somepony like you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:17.12,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,We may not see each other very often, but I know you will always be there when I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:19.48,Princess_Cadence,,0,0,0,,Just like she was there for you, Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:24.16,Discord,,0,0,0,,Yes, she is a real sweetheart. We are all so lucky to have her in our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.66,Discord,,0,0,0,,What in the World?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:47.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think it is pretty clear that my visit with Cadance didn't go quite the way I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:50.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But in the end I realised that when you are with a good friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:54.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,even the most chaotic day can end up being a great experience that brings you closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:57.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree, Discord?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.75,Discord,,0,0,0,,Yes, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:02.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go sayin' you got what you deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.05,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, I have no trouble saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You got what you deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:09.43,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Now now, he has learned his lession.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:12.00,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, my little patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.87,Discord,,0,0,0,,I am so glad that you are back from your trip, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:18.24,Discord,,0,0,0,,Just your presence here is making me feel so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.43,0:21:24.21,Discord,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering, could I trouble you for just one more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:25.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:31.28,Discord,,0,0,0,,What? I was simply going to ask for a teeny tiny glass of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:35.97,Somepony,,0,0,0,,СЧАСТЛИВЫЙ ПОНЕЦ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:39.26,Somepony,,0,0,0,,anon2anon\Nsunnysubs.com
